lines.text:
[after a lazy cuckoo emerges from his clock and rings a triangle for a dinner bell]
Is that duck ready yet, Maw?
No, and I don't think he ever will be. I keep a-lightin' the matches and he keeps a-blowin' them out!
[as Maw lights each match, Daffy sticks his head out of the oven and blows them out. Fade out]
